name: Maha
description: MAHA (previously known as MahaDAO) is a decentralized collective founded in 2020, building at the intersection of money, culture, and community. MAHA have pioneered innovations in stablecoins, decentralized governance, and incentive design. Today, we’re powering **WAGMIE**, a social network for internet culture — where anyone can launch tokens, build communities, and own the value they create. The $MAHA token serves as the core asset driving this ecosystem forward.
